This example is devoted to linking the checkpointing library with other 
softwares build externally with makefile. 

The user may modify the following parameters in other software package,
either by reading from parameter files, or from command line feeding.
  integer(c_int) :: info = 3, snaps = 5, steps = 15 ! needs to be specified

To compile: 	make
To run: 		./test
To clean: 		make clean

